    Class Description
    AllenBrainController
    The AllenBrainController is an abstraction for all endpoints of the Allen Brain Atlas
    AllenBrainService
    The AllenBrainService calls the allen brain atlas rest api, to get information needed for the atlas core service
    AtlasCoreApplication  
    AuthorizationHeaderInterceptor
    This interceptor is used to extract the Authorization header from the incoming request If an Authorization header is set, it will be stored in the RequestContextService
    CachingConfig
    Cache for data from external apis
    ControllerPaths
    All paths as a constant value
    CustomWebConfiguration
    Enables CORS requests
    DatasetsController  
    FilenameService  
    InterceptorAppConfig
    Configures all interceptors used in the application
    JsonObjectService  
    KnowledgeGraphController
    The AtlasCoreController is an abstraction for all endpoints of the AtlasCore Webservice
    KnowledgeGraphService
    The KnowledgeGraphService is used for the communication with the external KnowledgeGraph.
    Parcellation
    Representation of a Parcellation
    ParcellationController
    Controller to deliver a list of all parcellations for a referencespace and details to one parcellation by name and referencespace
    ParcellationRepository
    Repository for all parcellations in a given referencespace At the moment the data is read from files
    ParcellationResource
    Resource to wrap a parcellation and add HATEOAS support with link to all regions and a self link
    ParcellationService
    Service to communicate with all kind of repository sources, to get parcellations and details The service decides from the given referencespace which repository should be used
    Referencespace
    Representation of a Referencespace
    ReferencespaceController
    Controller to deliver a list of valid referencespaces and more details to one referencespace by id
    ReferencespaceRepository
    Static Repository with all referencespaces that are valid at the moment
    ReferencespaceResource
    Resource to wrap a referencespace and add HATEOAS support with link to all parcellations and a self link
    ReferencespaceService
    Service to communicate with all kind of repository sources, to get referencespaces and details ReferencespaceRepository
    Region
    Representation of a Region When converted to JSON, only not null properties will be included A Region with values can only be build by a RegionBuilder
    RegionBuilder  
    RegionController
    Controller to deliver a list of valid regions for a parcellation and more details to one region by name
    RegionRepository
    Repository for all regions for in a given parcellation and referencespace The data is stored in static files
    RegionResource
    Resource to wrap a Region and add HATEOAS support with a self link
    RegionService
    Service to communicate with all kind of repository sources and other services, to get regions and details The service decides from the given referencespace and parcellation which repository or service should be used
    RequestContextService
    The RequestContextService is used to store request information.
    RestResponseEntityExceptionHandler
    Exceptions handling for HttpClientErrorException which can be thrown by the RestTemplate The exceptions are rewritten to fit the spring boot default error response
    RestTemplateConfiguration
    This configuration creates a custom RestTemplate with interceptors to extend the outgoing requests.
    RestTemplateRequestInterceptor
    An interceptor for the custom RestTemplate bean.
    StaticPageController
    Controller for the static pages of the application
    SwaggerConfig
    Configuration for the swagger documentation
    TractLength
    Representation of a tract length
    TVBDummyDataService
    Service to read TVB example data from files and convert them to Region
    TVBService
    Service to deliver data from connectivity app
    Vector
    Representation of a vector with x, y, z values
    Weights
    Representation of weights
